    // Dialogue text box
    panel DialogueBox {
      position: [0.5, 0.18, 0]
      size: [0.6, 0.18]
      style: {
        background: '#1a1a2eEE'
        border: '2px solid #4a4a6a'
        borderRadius: '0 0 8 8'
        padding: 20
      }

      text SubtitleText {
        content: '{subtitleText}'
        color: '#FFFFFF'
        fontSize: 16
        lineHeight: 1.4
        wrap: true
      }

      // Voice indicator
      panel VoiceIndicator {
        position: [0.95, 0.9, 0]
        size: [0.03, 0.15]
        visible: isVoicePlaying

        animation Pulse {
          property: 'opacity'
          from: 0.5
          to: 1
          duration: 0.3s
          loop: infinite
        }

        text {
          content: '🔊'
          fontSize: 14
        }
      }
    }

    // Choice buttons
    panel ChoicesPanel {
      position: [0.5, 0.02, 0]
      size: [0.6, 0.12]
      visible: currentNode?.choices and not isVoicePlaying

      list Choices {
        data: currentNode?.choices or []
        layout: 'vertical'
        gap: 4

        template ChoiceButton {
          button {
            size: [1, 0.22]
            text: '{item.text}'
            style: {
              background: '#2a2a4eCC'
              border: '1px solid #4a4a6a'
              borderRadius: 4
              textColor: '#FFFFFF'
              fontSize: 14
              textAlign: 'left'
              padding: '8 16'
            }

            // Highlight on hover
            on hover {
              set style.background: '#4a4a6e'
              set style.borderColor: '#8a8aaa'
            }

            // Relationship preview
            if item.relationship > 0 {
              text RelIndicator {
                position: [0.95, 0.5, 0]
                content: '+{item.relationship} ❤️'
                color: '#55FF55'
                fontSize: 10
              }
            } else if item.relationship < 0 {
              text RelIndicator {
                position: [0.95, 0.5, 0]
                content: '{item.relationship} 💔'
                color: '#FF5555'
                fontSize: 10
              }
            }

            on click {
              call selectChoice(item)
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }

    // Skip indicator
    text SkipHint {
      position: [0.5, 0.35, 0]
      content: '[Space to skip]'
      color: '#666666'
      fontSize: 12
      visible: isVoicePlaying
    }
  }

  // Skip voice line
  on key 'Space' {
    if inDialogue and isVoicePlaying {
      stop sound currentVoice
      set subtitleText: currentNode.text
      set isVoicePlaying: false
    }
  }

  // ==========================================
  // SAMPLE NPC
  // ==========================================

  object Blacksmith extends NPC {
    model: 'blacksmith.glb'
    position: [5, 0, 0]
    name: 'Garen'
    dialogueTreeId: 'blacksmith_intro'

    animation Idle {
      clip: 'idle'
      loop: true
    }

    // Hammering animation when not in dialogue
    on interval 5s {
      if not isTalking {
        play animation 'hammer' then 'idle'
        play sound 'anvil_hit.mp3' at self.position
      }
    }
  }
}
```

**Features included**:
- **Branching dialogue**: Tree structure with conditional nodes
- **Relationship system**: Choices affect NPC relationships
- **Quest integration**: Start/complete quests from dialogue
- **Emotion system**: NPCs animate based on dialogue emotion
- **Voice playback**: Audio with synced typewriter subtitles
- **Shop integration**: Open shop directly from dialogue
- **Reputation**: Faction-based reputation tracking
- **Cooldowns**: NPCs can refuse to talk after negative interactions
- **UI**: Full dialogue box with choices, speaker name, skip hint
